text: "Not Me, Not I" is a 2003 song by Australian singer Delta Goodrem and is the fourth single from her debut studio album Innocent Eyes. It went to number 1 in Australia, number 11 in New Zealand, number 14 in Scotland, number 18 in the United Kingdom, number 25 in Ireland and number 49 in the Netherlands.
